&lt;section id="recording-signals"&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;Recording signals&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;section id="hardware"&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Hardware&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;I record using a USB sound card (&lt;a class="reference external" href="https://www.amazon.com/Adapter-CableCreation-External-Windows-Drivers/dp/B01H2XF8V8?th=1)"&gt;Cable Creation USB Audio External Sound Card&lt;/a&gt;).
The sensor is plugged into the microphone jack of the USB device.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/section&gt;
&lt;section id="software"&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Software&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;I record using a Linux command line program called &lt;code class="docutils literal"&gt;arecord&lt;/code&gt;.
To find the right parameters for the USB sound card, I run the following command which creates a list of installed audio devices.
As you can see, it is recognized as card 2, device 0.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class="code"&gt;&lt;pre class="code bash"&gt;&lt;a id="rest_code_4f6904b010964cb881796791f51cf1ed-1" name="rest_code_4f6904b010964cb881796791f51cf1ed-1" href="https://aubreymoore.github.io/blog2025/posts/recording-insect-wingbeat-waveforms/#rest_code_4f6904b010964cb881796791f51cf1ed-1"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;$&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;arecord&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;-l
&lt;a id="rest_code_4f6904b010964cb881796791f51cf1ed-2" name="rest_code_4f6904b010964cb881796791f51cf1ed-2" href="https://aubreymoore.github.io/blog2025/posts/recording-insect-wingbeat-waveforms/#rest_code_4f6904b010964cb881796791f51cf1ed-2"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;a id="rest_code_4f6904b010964cb881796791f51cf1ed-3" name="rest_code_4f6904b010964cb881796791f51cf1ed-3" href="https://aubreymoore.github.io/blog2025/posts/recording-insect-wingbeat-waveforms/#rest_code_4f6904b010964cb881796791f51cf1ed-3"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;List&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;of&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;CAPTURE&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;Hardware&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;Devices
&lt;a id="rest_code_4f6904b010964cb881796791f51cf1ed-4" name="rest_code_4f6904b010964cb881796791f51cf1ed-4" href="https://aubreymoore.github.io/blog2025/posts/recording-insect-wingbeat-waveforms/#rest_code_4f6904b010964cb881796791f51cf1ed-4"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;card&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="m"&gt;0&lt;/span&gt;:&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;PCH&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;[&lt;/span&gt;HDA&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;Intel&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;PCH&lt;span class="o"&gt;]&lt;/span&gt;,&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;device&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="m"&gt;0&lt;/span&gt;:&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;ALC1220&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;Analog&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;[&lt;/span&gt;ALC1220&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;Analog&lt;span class="o"&gt;]&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;a id="rest_code_4f6904b010964cb881796791f51cf1ed-5" name="rest_code_4f6904b010964cb881796791f51cf1ed-5" href="https://aubreymoore.github.io/blog2025/posts/recording-insect-wingbeat-waveforms/#rest_code_4f6904b010964cb881796791f51cf1ed-5"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;Subdevices:&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="m"&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;/1
&lt;a id="rest_code_4f6904b010964cb881796791f51cf1ed-6" name="rest_code_4f6904b010964cb881796791f51cf1ed-6" href="https://aubreymoore.github.io/blog2025/posts/recording-insect-wingbeat-waveforms/#rest_code_4f6904b010964cb881796791f51cf1ed-6"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;Subdevice&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="c1"&gt;#0: subdevice #0&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;a id="rest_code_4f6904b010964cb881796791f51cf1ed-7" name="rest_code_4f6904b010964cb881796791f51cf1ed-7" href="https://aubreymoore.github.io/blog2025/posts/recording-insect-wingbeat-waveforms/#rest_code_4f6904b010964cb881796791f51cf1ed-7"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;card&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="m"&gt;2&lt;/span&gt;:&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;Creation&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;[&lt;/span&gt;Cable&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;Creation&lt;span class="o"&gt;]&lt;/span&gt;,&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;device&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="m"&gt;0&lt;/span&gt;:&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;USB&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;Audio&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;[&lt;/span&gt;USB&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;Audio&lt;span class="o"&gt;]&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;a id="rest_code_4f6904b010964cb881796791f51cf1ed-8" name="rest_code_4f6904b010964cb881796791f51cf1ed-8" href="https://aubreymoore.github.io/blog2025/posts/recording-insect-wingbeat-waveforms/#rest_code_4f6904b010964cb881796791f51cf1ed-8"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;Subdevices:&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="m"&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;/1
&lt;a id="rest_code_4f6904b010964cb881796791f51cf1ed-9" name="rest_code_4f6904b010964cb881796791f51cf1ed-9" href="https://aubreymoore.github.io/blog2025/posts/recording-insect-wingbeat-waveforms/#rest_code_4f6904b010964cb881796791f51cf1ed-9"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;Subdevice&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="c1"&gt;#0: subdevice #0&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We can now record a 10 second audio file using the following command.
The parameters are:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul class="simple"&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;code class="docutils literal"&gt;&lt;span class="pre"&gt;-D&lt;/span&gt; hw:2,0&lt;/code&gt;: the device to record from (card 2, device 0)&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;code class="docutils literal"&gt;&lt;span class="pre"&gt;-d&lt;/span&gt; 10&lt;/code&gt;: the duration of the recording (10 seconds)&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;code class="docutils literal"&gt;&lt;span class="pre"&gt;-f&lt;/span&gt; dat&lt;/code&gt;: the format of the recording (dat) (16 bit little endian, 48000 Hz)&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;code class="docutils literal"&gt;&lt;span class="pre"&gt;-c&lt;/span&gt; 1&lt;/code&gt;: the number of channels (1 channel, mono)&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;div class="code"&gt;&lt;pre class="code bash"&gt;&lt;a id="rest_code_09eee2adf5e346d8a102b91b783586ed-1" name="rest_code_09eee2adf5e346d8a102b91b783586ed-1" href="https://aubreymoore.github.io/blog2025/posts/recording-insect-wingbeat-waveforms/#rest_code_09eee2adf5e346d8a102b91b783586ed-1"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;$&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;arecord&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;-D&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;hw:2,0&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;-d&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="m"&gt;10&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;-f&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;dat&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;-c&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="m"&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;audio.wav
&lt;a id="rest_code_09eee2adf5e346d8a102b91b783586ed-2" name="rest_code_09eee2adf5e346d8a102b91b783586ed-2" href="https://aubreymoore.github.io/blog2025/posts/recording-insect-wingbeat-waveforms/#rest_code_09eee2adf5e346d8a102b91b783586ed-2"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;a id="rest_code_09eee2adf5e346d8a102b91b783586ed-3" name="rest_code_09eee2adf5e346d8a102b91b783586ed-3" href="https://aubreymoore.github.io/blog2025/posts/recording-insect-wingbeat-waveforms/#rest_code_09eee2adf5e346d8a102b91b783586ed-3"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;Recording&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;WAVE&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="s1"&gt;'audio.wav'&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;:&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;Signed&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="m"&gt;16&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;bit&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;Little&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;Endian,&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;Rate&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="m"&gt;48000&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;Hz,&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;Mono
&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/section&gt;
